rows.label: qst700107_msg0001
rows.name:
You kannot run!
Give up, give up!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0002
rows.name: If Tirkin take kattle, Mother be pleased!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0003
rows.name: Everyone pleased! Rejoice, rejoice!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0004
rows.name:
I feel bad crashing your party, boys,
but we'll be having that Armu back.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0005
rows.name: You wot?!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm sorry, but there's a little boy who's
eagerly awaiting her return.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0007
rows.name:
You lie! Liar, liar, great big liar!
We find first!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0008
rows.name: You give proof! Give, give!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0009
rows.name:
Very well!
Let's see...

rows.label: qst700107_msg0010
rows.name:
Does either of you happen to remember
what her name was? Uhh... Nebbish?
Sheepish? No, hang on...

rows.label: qst700107_msg0011
rows.name:
Easy there, Prince.
You're embarrassing yourself.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0012
rows.name:
The three we were looking for were
Yonma, Ajijii, and then... Iwashisshi.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0013
rows.name:
...Yes, there's our Iwashisshi.
No doubt about it.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0014
rows.name:
The kid's good at training them,
I'll give him that.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0015
rows.name: Nonsense! Is mek no sense!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0016
rows.name:
Name sound like delicious!
Me hungry! Getting more hungry!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0017
rows.name: We take Armu! No kontest!

rows.label: qst700107_msg0018
rows.name:
...Oh, bother... I had really hoped to
resolve this peacefully.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0019
rows.name:
We tried, Your Majesty.
We tried.

rows.label: qst700107_msg0020
rows.name:
Fine, if this is how you want it...
Everyone! Protect the Armu!
